Notification-daemon-xfce is a port of Gnome's notification-daemon
for the Xfce desktop. It depends on the following packages:
  * gtk >= 2.6.0
  * libxfce4util >= 4.3.90
  * libxfcegui4 >= 4.3.90
  * dbus >= 0.36
  * libsexy >= 0.1.3
The Xfce version also uses xfce4-dev-tools for creating the make files.

More information about the origional version of the
notification-daemon can be found here:
  http://www.galago-project.org
